text: Treffort-Cuisiat is a former commune. It is found in the region Auvergne- Rhône-Alpes in the Ain department in the east of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Val-Revermont.Arrêté préfectoral 4 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Ain
title: Treffort-Cuisiat
